      <title>Should I release those visuals ? Maybe .tox ? Mostly made with #RayTK by @t3kt –...</title>
      <link>https://www.instagram.com/p/DVnurmAjeD9/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/649218715_933626665830929_7349346907241255499_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpegr_e15_p360x360_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=103&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg0ODI0OTcxMjQ5OTg3NjA5Mw%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjY0MHgxMTM2Lmhkci5DMyJ9&amp;_nc_ohc=SaRkKJZpyTcQ7kNvwGn1uKM&amp;_nc_oc=AdoS3ygTI3er__--_OP6f8KL2YOFX1cuNESLmfjLYx0HLq3xj7H_E7AW7lynQmPTbOo&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;se=-1&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=OaIoqzexGHqiZtI3cRftMA&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfyJcrzjlVbVcWfaBkkmTfcT_61oK3Kt1zo2adA7J4xjSA&amp;oe=69C8DD88" alt="Instagram billede fra @erez_arts" /></p><p><strong>@erez_arts</strong></p><p>Should I release those visuals ? Maybe .tox ? Mostly made with #RayTK by @t3kt – a toolkit for TouchDesigner that lets you create raymarching 3D shaders using nodes, without writing any GLSL code!<br/>
Probably my favorite tool to just jam visuals #touchdesigner #mediaart #vj #videomapping</p>]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/649218715_933626665830929_7349346907241255499_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpegr_e15_p360x360_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=103&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg0ODI0OTcxMjQ5OTg3NjA5Mw%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjY0MHgxMTM2Lmhkci5DMyJ9&amp;_nc_ohc=SaRkKJZpyTcQ7kNvwGn1uKM&amp;_nc_oc=AdoS3ygTI3er__--_OP6f8KL2YOFX1cuNESLmfjLYx0HLq3xj7H_E7AW7lynQmPTbOo&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;se=-1&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=OaIoqzexGHqiZtI3cRftMA&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfyJcrzjlVbVcWfaBkkmTfcT_61oK3Kt1zo2adA7J4xjSA&amp;oe=69C8DD88" alt="Instagram billede fra @erez_arts" /></p><p><strong>@erez_arts</strong></p><p>Should I release those visuals ? Maybe .tox ? Mostly made with #RayTK by @t3kt – a toolkit for TouchDesigner that lets you create raymarching 3D shaders using nodes, without writing any GLSL code!<br/>
Probably my favorite tool to just jam visuals #touchdesigner #mediaart #vj #videomapping</p>]]></content:encoded>
