      <description><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/643559507_1843448959929047_7317717531339977911_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpegr_e15_p360x360_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=105&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg0MDM2MTkxNzI5OTEyMDI5OQ%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjY0MHgxMTM2Lmhkci5DMyJ9&amp;_nc_ohc=FjKMlFLd0-YQ7kNvwFo1S2W&amp;_nc_oc=Adqss8-gHvEveFKMX5ca5QFGUaWiUd5wPKAfU0fiTstqPG812oFW8dP5HRfT6LuOccw&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;se=-1&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=OaIoqzexGHqiZtI3cRftMA&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfyS7CWBGT__g5oqv2eQ165JpiETg4iSaU3TJiOcnyiZMg&amp;oe=69C90F92" alt="Instagram billede fra @erez_arts" /></p><p><strong>@erez_arts</strong></p><p>Using my Ai painter app for Video mapping . This is an app I developed using @touchdesigner and stream diffusion. Giving the visitors to control how much ai influence they want over their painting turns this experience to a collaboration of human touch and Ai art in real time.<br/>
#videomapping #aicoding #vibecoding #touchdesigner #aiart</p>]]></description>
      <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><img src="https://scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/643559507_1843448959929047_7317717531339977911_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpegr_e15_p360x360_tt6&amp;_nc_cat=105&amp;ig_cache_key=Mzg0MDM2MTkxNzI5OTEyMDI5OQ%3D%3D.3-ccb7-5&amp;ccb=7-5&amp;_nc_sid=58cdad&amp;efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6InhwaWRzLjY0MHgxMTM2Lmhkci5DMyJ9&amp;_nc_ohc=FjKMlFLd0-YQ7kNvwFo1S2W&amp;_nc_oc=Adqss8-gHvEveFKMX5ca5QFGUaWiUd5wPKAfU0fiTstqPG812oFW8dP5HRfT6LuOccw&amp;_nc_ad=z-m&amp;_nc_cid=0&amp;_nc_zt=23&amp;se=-1&amp;_nc_ht=scontent-cph2-1.cdninstagram.com&amp;_nc_gid=OaIoqzexGHqiZtI3cRftMA&amp;_nc_ss=7a338&amp;oh=00_AfyS7CWBGT__g5oqv2eQ165JpiETg4iSaU3TJiOcnyiZMg&amp;oe=69C90F92" alt="Instagram billede fra @erez_arts" /></p><p><strong>@erez_arts</strong></p><p>Using my Ai painter app for Video mapping . This is an app I developed using @touchdesigner and stream diffusion. Giving the visitors to control how much ai influence they want over their painting turns this experience to a collaboration of human touch and Ai art in real time.<br/>
#videomapping #aicoding #vibecoding #touchdesigner #aiart</p>]]></content:encoded>
